Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:05.88,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Once upon a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:09.98,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,a kind-hearted red ogre lived all by himself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:12.35,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:18.90,SignA,Sign 0013,0000,0000,0000,,Home to a kind-hearted ogre. \NAll are welcome. \NDelicious sweets and tea available.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:18.91,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming friends with humans \Nwas his constant desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:23.41,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.58,0:00:40.13,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,They were afraid of the ogre and stayed far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:48.63,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,The red ogre's friend, the blue ogre, \Ncame to him and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:51.26,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,"Say, Red...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:53.91,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,How about I stir things up in the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:56.95,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,You can defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:01:02.20,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Then the humans should rethink who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:05.46,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,and you can become friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:00.76,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Gouda Takeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:02.03,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a third-year in junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:05.41,SignB,Sign 0303,0000,0000,0000,,30th Graduation Ceremony \NShuuei Junior High School
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:05.41,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Today is my last day in junior high,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:07.32,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,the graduation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.53,0:03:17.09,Default - italics,Student,0000,0000,0000,,And now, it's time for farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:23.69,Default - italics,Student,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:26.47,Title1,Sign 0324,0000,0000,0000,,My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:28.97,Default,Friend,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:31.71,Default,Friend,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad we won't be in the same high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:32.55,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:35.23,Default,Friend,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we could've gone to the same school!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:35.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:37.51,Default,Friend,0000,0000,0000,,Keep in touch, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:38.61,Default,Friend,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:38.98,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:39.86,Default,Underclassman,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:41.20,Default,Underclassman,0000,0000,0000,,Osu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:41.95,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.51,Default,U,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for being with the club for three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:47.16,Default,U,0000,0000,0000,,Please come by sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:47.66,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:51.82,SignC,Sign 0324,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything \N—Shinonara Ippon! \N\NThank you! —Nomura \N\NYou're the man!! \N\NYou're my role model \N\NTo Takeo-senpai \NCongratulations on your graduation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:50.08,Default,U,0000,0000,0000,,This is from all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:55.37,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Make it to nationals this year, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:56.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:03:57.36,Default,U,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:03:58.16,Default,U,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:03:58.96,Default,U,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:03:59.97,Default,U,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:00.96,Default,U,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.30,Default,Students,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:03.72,Default,Students,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takeo! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:04.47,Default,Students,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:08.62,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've been working with Satou-san \Nin the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:10.50,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's kind and has a great smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:11.56,Default - italics,Satou,0000,0000,0000,,Gouda-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:15.20,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Before I graduate, I want to tell her how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:17.98,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Satou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:22.82,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Satou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:26.65,Default,Satou,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:31.62,Default,Satou,0000,0000,0000,,I've always liked you, Sunakawa-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:38.34,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any feelings for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:43.38,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Takeo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:44.30,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:46.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:48.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:50.25,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:05:00.64,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is my friend, Sunakawa Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:03.53,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we friends, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:05.54,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:09.78,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,When is the high school entrance ceremony again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:11.85,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,April 7th, I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:13.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, the 6th...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.48,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Around there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.97,0:05:16.09,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You lazy bum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:21.33,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna's super popular with the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:25.15,Default - flashback,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Sunakawa-kun's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:26.93,Default - flashback,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen him laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.54,Default - flashback,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that be great?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:30.88,Default - flashback,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he only laughs for girls he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:31.95,Default - flashback,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,That's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:32.68,Default - flashback,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:35.28,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,When we graduated from kindergarten,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:37.19,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,the girl I liked, Yuzuha-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.06,Default - flashback,Yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I like you a lot, Sunakawa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:40.81,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.86,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,With that, he made her cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:45.18,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make girls cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:46.32,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:47.36,Default - flashback,Yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:50.90,SignD,Sign 0548,0000,0000,0000,,See? I apologized.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:51.86,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same story in elementary school \Nwith the girl I liked, Misaki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:52.65,Default - flashback,Misaki,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:53.63,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:54.79,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,And for Kayomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:55.47,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:56.60,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,And Eriha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:57.31,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:58.41,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,And Mao-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:05:59.49,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Dislike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:02.96,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,All of them fall for Suna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:07.22,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,People often ask why I'm friends with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:08.98,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,We live in the same apartment complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:12.56,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,We're neighbors, and our moms are friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:14.58,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,As kids, we played together a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:15.96,Default - flashback,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:18.35,Default - flashback,SMom,0000,0000,0000,,Come in! Sorry for the mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:19.61,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:21.01,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Real men should fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:23.04,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for a face-off, man! \NHow do you wanna do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:23.65,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:24.28,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sword fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:25.04,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Card game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:26.33,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:27.19,SignE,Sign 0627,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(68,1)}Achooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.36,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Even though our moms got along,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:28.94,SignE,Sign 0628,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(68,1)}Wa-chaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:31.30,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,that isn't to say that we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:30.19,SignE,Sign 0629,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(68,1)}Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:32.95,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Video game, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:32.26,SignE,Sign 0632,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(68,1)}Laser Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:33.57,SignE,Sign 0633,0000,0000,0000,,Def not on the same wavelength...      Laser Beam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:33.58,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:34.78,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:36.33,SignF,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,601)}I can't see
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:35.68,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:37.20,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why can I not win?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:37.99,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Because you suck?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:38.85,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:40.04,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.01,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:42.28,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:44.78,SignF,Sign 0644,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(1,334)}I can't see
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:44.06,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,We never fought, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.06,0:06:45.50,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Man, another loss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.57,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,I lost again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:52.20,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,And so on and so forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:54.51,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Till the present day. I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:56.92,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's Sunakawa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:58.09,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he comes through here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:06:59.89,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sunakawa-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:02.40,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wasn't that guy super hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:04.61,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Suna...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:05.37,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:09.40,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that there's been \Na prowler around here lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.63,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:20.15,School,Sign 0712,0000,0000,0000,,Shisuda Municipal Elementary School
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:13.43,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:14.70,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is he after kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:16.44,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,How dare he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.94,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I got kind of hung up over it, so yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:28.67,School,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Shisuda Municipal \NElementary School
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:30.17,SignD,Sign 0729,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.73,SignG,Sign 0731,0000,0000,0000,,He makes me nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:35.42,Default - flashback,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:39.85,Default - flashback,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,We got a call that there's a scary guy \Nstanding at the school gates...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:44.13,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,So yesterday, I got reported to the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:51.68,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Girls, this is how he looks when he laughs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:07:58.25,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to laugh so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:07:59.62,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:03.08,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Not that it's a big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:09.49,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, we're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:14.26,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:16.08,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,That was smooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:19.38,SignB,Sign 0818,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\c&H656566&\fad(906,1)}Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:17.20,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Nice job!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:18.54,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,He's a real pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:28.01,SignH,Sign 0827,0000,0000,0000,,Ignored?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:29.23,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:31.90,Default,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:37.66,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just not a smooth customer like Suna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:39.24,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.61,0:08:43.16,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That guy... Isn't he kinda sketchy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:48.99,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:57.88,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Get off this train at the next station!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:02.23,Default,Perv,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:04.08,Default,Perv,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:14.21,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:18.74,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.67,0:09:20.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:23.13,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:41.60,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you take losers like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.66,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do we just leave him with \Nsomeone who works here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:47.73,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take things from here, so you can—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.52,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:52.33,Default,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,A groper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:54.72,SignB,Sign 0953,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\c&H424F45&}You again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:55.17,Default,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who caught him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:55.82,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:58.24,Default,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you can let go of him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:09:59.69,Default,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see what he has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:00.56,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:04.41,Default,Perv,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:05.64,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.11,Default,Perv,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:10.65,Default,Perv,0000,0000,0000,,Officer, this guy hurt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:11.93,Default,Perv,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:14.03,Default,Perv,0000,0000,0000,,He grabbed my arm, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:16.08,Default,Perv,0000,0000,0000,,Then he did a number on my neck, like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:16.93,Default,Perv,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:17.84,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,He groped me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:22.47,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,This man helped me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:23.66,Default,Perv,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:26.60,Default,Perv,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking, with your skirt up to there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:29.64,Default,Perv,0000,0000,0000,,You were really asking for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:40.49,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell she was, you scumbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:48.25,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:52.16,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I got suspended.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:53.48,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:56.17,SignH,Sign 1056,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\an9\c&H586463&}Door was open, but just in case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:01.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo, here are the notes from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:03.98,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Not that you'd study anyway, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:19.32,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, Suna!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:20.82,Gouda,Sign 1120,0000,0000,0000,,Gouda!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:21.66,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.76,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd go after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:25.63,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I kinda thought you might...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:26.77,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Then cut me some slack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:30.46,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I totally didn't think you'd slug \Nhim in front of a cop, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he pissed me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:32.47,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:34.27,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:34.31,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:35.65,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Take!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:37.60,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,A girl's here to see you! A girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:39.21,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,She says she's Yamato-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:40.26,Default,TMom,0000,0000,0000,,Can she come up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.05,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Yamato?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.41,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:47.14,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone from our junior high?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:49.48,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:51.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,you sure you're okay with a girl in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:59.51,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Ask her to wait one sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:02.61,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm already here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:13.08,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for helping me yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:19.97,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:24.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:25.64,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:27.64,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.86,0:12:28.68,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:31.53,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,This again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:33.99,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,No surprise there, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:37.25,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um, here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:39.38,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I brought this to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:42.38,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it might be better to \Nshare it with more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:46.88,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, maybe you don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:50.20,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, maybe you think I'm creepy \Nbecause I came over without asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.58,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I asked at the train station yesterday, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.29,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:12:59.41,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:07.82,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What is this deliciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:09.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of cake is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.03,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's cheesecake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.03,0:13:12.67,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You've never had one before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:13.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:15.60,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But now that you mention it, I taste the cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:17.14,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:20.32,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:24.36,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll really get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:28.12,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I guess I should get going, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:33.75,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who helped you out, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:38.00,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:41.05,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess I kind of went \Noff the rails at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:42.69,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:45.76,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I got a cake out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:50.78,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,And it was good, so it's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:54.37,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I helped a girl who turned out to be a nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:57.22,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,That gives me the strength to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:01.11,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,End of story!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:19.24,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this pink cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:23.80,Phone,Sign 1422,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming Call \N{\fs20}Public Phone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:22.24,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Suna's?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:25.46,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:26.23,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:27.68,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I thought so!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:30.90,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I forgot my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:34.54,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm Yamato from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:36.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's with me, at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:37.78,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:39.66,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.66,0:14:41.64,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,When would be a good day for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:44.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I can just bring it to you, if you tell me where.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:48.40,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about we pick a time and place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:49.99,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I go to Koizumi Girls Academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:52.51,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,so how about we meet in front of \Nthe fountain in Shisuda Park?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:54.45,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:56.58,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um, how about tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:57.75,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:15:00.70,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}After school, around three o'clock?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:00.70,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it isn't "end of story" yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:04.60,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the smartphone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:05.40,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:07.75,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The girl from yesterday forgot it at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:10.34,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to return it to her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:11.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:15.06,SignC,Sign 1513,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(169,604)\an9\c&H403E28&}Good luck
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:15.01,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,That girl, Yamato-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:18.35,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she's expecting Suna to show up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:20.85,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she saw him with me both times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:23.46,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:25.06,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:26.49,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Just come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:28.90,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,No worries...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:30.59,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring him with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:33.13,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's what real men do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:45.04,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:46.38,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:48.61,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to be so polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:50.88,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,We're the same year, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.11,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Both high school first-years?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:52.99,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:55.14,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:57.41,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one being polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:15:59.02,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's to thank you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:05.41,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to thank you for taking the \Ntrouble to bring me my phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:08.88,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, we can find a seat and eat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:16.42,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's this amazing deliciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.42,0:16:18.28,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of food is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:19.58,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Macaroons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.01,0:16:21.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Macaroons are delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:25.03,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:27.38,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I baked these.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:28.34,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The cake last time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:32.01,SignH - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:31.13,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,They're home-baked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:32.12,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You mean "homemade."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.97,SignH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(104,1)}{\fs14}Pretty sure that's wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:33.84,SignH - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,Munch, Munch
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:34.97,SignH - Copy,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:37.72,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good at baking, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:39.71,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Good at baking...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.11,0:16:40.85,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Baking...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:42.10,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Baking...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:45.99,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true you need stamina to make sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:46.74,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:48.23,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You have to mix a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:49.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Mix a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:51.91,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,A lot... A lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:54.95,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:17:00.36,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you blushing and nervous all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:02.12,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:05.21,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like Suna that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:06.26,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Stop staring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:08.54,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're invading her personal space.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:20.53,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Off to the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:22.64,SignD,Sign 1721,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H22704B&}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:28.33,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't human emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:29.91,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,not even my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:32.03,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,work out the way we want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:35.53,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Am I just naïve?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:38.28,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,No point in developing feelings for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:40.80,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It'll just make things awkward for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:44.16,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's a good idea, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:49.30,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Your head's soaking wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:50.92,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I have a towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:57.91,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:00.97,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:03.43,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,If this girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:06.91,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,If Yamato-san gets heartbroken and cries,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.34,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be really sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:14.05,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I want to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,0:18:16.91,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.29,0:18:19.75,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to eat cake again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:22.78,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be possible for you to bake another?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:24.87,SignI,Sign 1824,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(217,1)\c&HD9E9D8&}Dude, that came outta nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.09,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You'd let me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:27.00,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:31.07,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The next one I'm good at \Nwould be a sachertorte.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:31.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:32.84,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like sachertorte?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:39.33,SignB,Sign 1834,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\c&H4B4B16&} serious face
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:36.04,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I love sacherotote.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:39.34,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, you totally faked knowing what it even is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:42.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, next time, sachertorte!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:43.98,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:48.47,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you in any way I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:59.06,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,She told me that when she bakes, \Nshe doesn't use a hand mixer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:00.37,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:03.87,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,She likes going through the extra trouble \Nand seeing it all come together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:05.38,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:06.86,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:10.65,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:12.55,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,kind of nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:23.00,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've heard Suna \Nsay something nice about a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:25.88,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:37.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:41.43,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I made it back in... time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.64,0:19:43.28,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:44.38,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:45.33,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.67,0:19:46.98,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:50.51,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:53.88,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Your e-mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know your e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:58.87,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I need it to contact you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:04.01,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me your e-mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:07.00,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She sprinted back
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:10.03,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,as fast as she could.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:12.45,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's totally sweaty...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:19.30,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Am I that sweaty?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:20.32,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:20.94,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll dry off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:21.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:24.29,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You can keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:37.72,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:39.42,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, just use infrared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:45.53,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:11.45,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,You really like Suna, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:17.19,Planner,Sign 2116,0000,0000,0000,,Student Planner
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.65,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,All right, my mind's made up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:19.80,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be your cheerleader.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:23.33,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.51,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.48,0:21:32.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the old-school washcloth?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:35.30,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,My mom likes 'em.
